{"tid":651840,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【封路大塞車】中國女危坐簷篷自殘 掛橫額「申訴無門 香港同胞對不起」","createTime":"2018-05-03T11:53:22.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-04T04:39:32.000Z","uid":39464,"like":4,"dislike":149,"uniUserReply":83,"replies":[{"pid":"2c92fb12db9fca3779f8016fd97d66a21b2fec6e","tid":651840,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-03T11:53:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180503/large/1525347445_5594.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180503%2Flarge%2F1525347445_5594.jpg&h=0198801f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180503/large/1525347447_114a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180503%2Flarge%2F1525347447_114a.jpg&h=347ffc59&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【19:30】危坐女子為內地人<br />\n【19:20】彌敦道南行近永星里慢線仍然封閉，車龍龍尾已到太子道西<br />\n【18:50】女事主自行返回安全位置<br />\n【18:35】彌敦道南行近永星里快線解封，但中線及慢線仍然封閉<br />\n【18:30】彌敦道南行的車龍龍尾已到界限街<br />\n<br />\n傍晚近6時，一名內地女子持刀於油麻地近永星里簷篷危坐，並掛起寫上簡體字的橫額，稱「孤兒寡婦，上訪十年申訴無門，香港同胞我對不起你們」，其間她情緒激動割手自殘。消防於地面張開救生氣墊戒備，警方派出談判專家游說，並將彌敦道南行近永星里3線全封，交通嚴重擠塞。彌敦道南行的車龍龍尾一度到界限街。<br />\n至晚上近7時，女事主態度軟化，自行返回安全位置，再乘救護車送院檢查。<br />\n<br />\n24小時求助熱線︰<br />\n香港撒瑪利亞防止自殺會熱線︰23892222<br />\n撒瑪利亞會熱線(多種語言)︰28960000<br />\n生命熱線︰23820000<br />\n東華三院芷若園熱線︰18281<br />\n社會福利署熱線︰23432255<br />\n醫院管理局精神健康專線(24小時精神健康熱線諮詢服務)：24667350<br />\n明愛向晴熱線：18288<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20180503/58148721\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180503%2F58148721&d=xEcxK8RUtCiVCfvhxqzm58VakpCEQgWe3bOYm8oES40%3D&h=016ae5ae\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180503%2F58148721&h=1c8c2e7e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20180503/58148721</a>"},{"pid":"d029cfdad7d5115675b165e354148b66b1250495","tid":651840,"uid":30169,"like":82,"dislike":2,"score":80,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-03T11:54:35.000Z","msg":"上到大陸人間蒸發"},{"pid":"3466f5f355d82214bf14c90c21829cb82601654e","tid":651840,"uid":22913,"like":113,"dislike":8,"score":105,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-03T11:55:58.000Z","msg":"死你就死啦 阻Q住曬"},{"pid":"a1cda73ae0503a36b19eacaabbbfeb8c4351a683","tid":651840,"uid":30006,"like":57,"dislike":3,"score":54,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-03T11:57:58.000Z","msg":"阻住地球轉，你返中國慢慢坐啦仆街"},{"pid":"58e670221973b6d367114473d46af64e311ae005","tid":651840,"uid":79442,"like":89,"dislike":1,"score":88,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-03T11:58:00.000Z","msg":"多d大陸人學佢中共會唔會嚴格d審查來港人士?"},{"pid":"5298b525addc2ca738a5f418bd8813ca2d4d6734","tid":651840,"uid":24730,"like":141,"dislike":3,"score":138,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2018-05-03T11:58:46.000Z","msg":"其實支那上訪無門既人如果都嚟晒香港示威，都係好事"},{"pid":"aa52a427c99691c37b4742f377d459b25b1f3525","tid":651840,"uid":118120,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-03T11:58:48.000Z","msg":"大陸人係唔係咁呀<br />\n連死都要連累香港人一獲"},{"pid":"04ac355df506d6f202d5b2dbdaa34c965cb3989c","tid":651840,"uid":53122,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-03T11:59:14.000Z","msg":"變左嚟香港上訪"},{"pid":"75348a74395779b5b8736cacde080710066bbd7f","tid":651840,"uid":6347,"like":27,"dislike":0,"score":27,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-03T11:59:44.000Z","msg":"係都學下寫繁體先啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9ecbdc5545b5290a12497b7bd5a10d9ee7d90e8","tid":651840,"uid":29514,"like":82,"dislike":2,"score":80,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-03T11:59:48.000Z","msg":"邊撚個同你同胞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 死撚開啦"},{"pid":"089e5c10aab99b3205832d40260b3b54d435db42","tid":651840,"uid":76776,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-03T12:00:1